<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/374292-is-this-book-connected-to-american-gods">Is this book connected to AMERICAN GODS? Should I read this series in order?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_374292'><a id="like_count_community_question_374292" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/374292?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">23 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2744.Anansi_Boys">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/374292-is-this-book-connected-to-american-gods">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/374292-is-this-book-connected-to-american-gods">See all 7 answers</a>
