              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22106879-jayson?shelf=genre-comedy">genre-comedy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22106879-jayson?shelf=300-399-pp">300-399-pp</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer683649247" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4727060157834100445"><b>(B+) 76%</b> | Good<br/><i>Notes:</i> Little transition between its real-world first half and its magical second half. Its story gets all wishy-washy at the end.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


