              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68155245-bea?shelf=gaiman">gaiman</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68155245-bea?shelf=3-star-reads">3-star-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68155245-bea?shelf=read-in-2018">read-in-2018</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2584920537" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1215776131867910889">3 stars I guess. Got kind of distracted towards the end but understood the gist of the story.</span>

          </span>
